description:
On this journey to the archaeological remains of the stunning city of Petra, visit many of the Bible’s important landmarks. Ponder the fate of Lot’s disobedient wife, explore the traditional burial place of faithful Job, and admire the deep red rocks of Petra—the amazing city whose discovery agrees with what the Bible has said all along. Does Petra in the Bible have anything to teach us in the 21st century? Francois DuPlessis presents these remarkable lessons from the past that help us navigate through our Christian experience today.

Watch more: https://adtv.watch/

Subscribe to our YouTube channel: https://www.youtube.com/user/OfficialADTVChannel?sub_confirmation=1

Visit our website: https://new.amazingdiscoveries.org/
